description:
Versione SII-H-OIII-LRGB  palette della nebulosa rosetta in monoceros 
ottenuta con 80triplet tecnosky con 
focheggiatore elettronico, ridotto a 380mm 
con reducer flattener 0.8x , CCD starlight SXVR-h16 operante a -25c°
su Montatura EQ6 eqmodded autoguidata con orion SSAG e 
scopos 66 tutto controllato da voyager softaware,
pose da : Halfa 6nm 10x900sec bin 1x1 , SII 10x900 sec bin 1x1, OIII 10x900 sec bin 1x1 CLSccd 10x900 sec bin 1x1, RGB 10x300sec bin 1x1 per ogni canale 
elaborazione con maxim Dl e photoshop. 
SII-H-OIII-LRGB version of the rosette nebula in monoceros
Obtained with tecnosky 80 with
Electronic focuser, reduced to 380mm with 0.8x flattener reducer, starlight SXVR-h16 CCD operating at -25c °German equatorial mount EQ6 eqmodded autogued with orion SSAG e
Scopos 66 all controlled by voyager software,
subframe : Halfa 6nm 10x900sec bin 1x1, SII 10x900 sec bin 1x1, OIII 10x900 sec bin 1x1, CLSccdc 10x900 sec bin 1x1 RGB 10x300 sec bin 1x1 for each RGB channel
Processing with maxim Dl and photoshop.
title: NGC2244  SII-H-OIII -LRGB palette
